                                 </label>

                        </div>

         (function() {
            var purl = window.location.href;

            var profileVersionId = '';

            if ( purl.indexOf('pwtv=')>0 ) {

         (function() {
            var purl = window.location.href;

            var profileVersionId = '';

            if ( purl.indexOf('pwtv=')>0 ) {

               function destroyAdhesion(slotName) {
                  console.log(`rym.ads: calling destroySlot on div-gpt-ad-${slotName}`)

            <script  type="module" id="module_dep_share">
                import * as share from 'https://e.snmc.io/dist/js/page/section/share.mjs?v=940147aa-274d-4661-9036-a5450fd0356a';
                window.page = window.page || {};
                window.page.section = window.page.section || {};
                window.page.section.share = share;


            if ( window.page.section.share._initPage !== undefined ) {
               rymQ(window.page.section.share._initPage);
            }
            </script>

            <script  type="module" id="module_dep_media_links">
                import * as media_links from 'https://e.snmc.io/dist/js/ui/media_links.mjs?v=940147aa-274d-4661-9036-a5450fd0356a';
                window.ui = window.ui || {};
                window.ui.media_links = media_links;


            if ( window.ui.media_links._initPage !== undefined ) {
               rymQ(window.ui.media_links._initPage);
            }
            </script>

         <script>

           window.addEventListener('load', (event) => {

               for ( var i in window.ryminit ) {
                  var fn = window.ryminit[i];
                  window.ryminit[i] = null;
                  if ( fn ) {
                     fn();
                  }
               }

               window.ryminit = null;
            });

         </script>
